meta.sourceNote: Compiled from public indicators and proxies

indicators.name: Singapore interest rate proxy
indicators.why: Higher rates increase debt service burden and raise refinancing risk for leveraged developers.

indicators.name: Corporate credit spread proxy
indicators.why: Wider spreads can indicate tighter financing conditions and more expensive debt issuance.

indicators.name: Construction cost inflation proxy
indicators.why: Persistent cost inflation compresses margins and elevates execution risk for ongoing projects.

indicators.name: Office vacancy proxy
indicators.why: Rising vacancy can weaken rental income and asset valuations, reducing cash flow flexibility.

indicators.name: Singapore manufacturing/services PMI blend
indicators.why: Slower business activity can pressure demand, leasing momentum and buyer confidence.

indicators.name: Private home price index growth
indicators.why: Decelerating or negative price growth can weaken sell-through rates and inventory monetization.
